title: International Livestock Research Institude, Kenya - Road Network, Kenya, 1978 - 1997
name: International Livestock Research Institude, Kenya - Road Network, Kenya, 1978 - 1997
description: This coverage shows the road networks of Kenya derived from topographic map sheets (1978-1997). This Dataset was found online at http://www.ilri.org/gis/ and was uploaded as a polyline shapefile.
